description: Sutskever’s departure after nearly a decade at the company ends months of speculation in Silicon Valley about the future of a top AI researcher who played a key role in the brief ouster of Sam Altman last year.
title: OpenAI’s Co-Founder and Chief Scientist Ilya Sutskever Is Leaving the Company

description: “The ban is a pernicious attack on free speech,” a lawyer for the creators said, while a Justice Dept. spokesperson said the government looks forward to defending the law in court.
title: A Group of TikTok Creators Are Suing the U.S. to Block a Potential Ban on the App
